OL,3,C'Find the words' - the push to get
OL,4,Cpeople talking about baby loss
OL,6,FA campaign has now been launched to
OL,7,Fget more people talking about its
OL,8,Fimpact on families and the stigma
OL,9,Faround it.
OL,11,FThe charity behind it, Sands, launched
OL,12,Fits "Finding the Words" scheme to help
OL,13,Feveryone feel more confident to start
OL,14,Fthese important conversations.
OL,16,FRuth Mason's sons George and Henry
OL,17,Fwere stillborn in August 2018.
OL,19,FShe told ITV Cymru Wales, "Any parent
OL,20,Fwho has gone through baby loss finds
OL,21,Fit hard to find the words."
