OL,3,C'Find the words' - the push to get
OL,4,Cpeople talking about baby loss
OL,6,F"It's all about supporting people to
OL,7,Fknow what to say to make people feel
OL,8,Fless vulnerable and lonely and
OL,9,Fisolated during what already is a very
OL,10,Fdifficult time."
OL,12,FBut what is the right thing to say?
OL,13,FThat is the basis of the Sands
OL,14,Fcampaign which wants to encourage
OL,15,Fpeople to 'Find the Words'.
