OL,3,C'Find the words' - the push to get
OL,4,Cpeople talking about baby loss
OL,6,FThe charity's CEO, Clea Hamer, said,
OL,7,F"The most important thing to remember
OL,8,Fis it's the reaching out that's
OL,9,Fimportant and that you're never going
OL,10,Fto make it better and you can't make
OL,11,Fit better - what you're trying to do
OL,12,Fis just be with that person", she said.
OL,14,F"It's really important to acknowledge
OL,15,Fif you're feeling anxious and worried
OL,16,Fso saying things like: 'I'm so sorry,
OL,17,FI don't know what to say' is actually
OL,18,Fbetter than saying nothing at all.
