OL,3,C'Find the words' - the push to get
OL,4,Cpeople talking about baby loss
OL,6,FOften asking about the baby, asking if
OL,7,Fthe baby has had a name, asking how
OL,8,Fthey are doing asking if you can help
OL,9,F- all of the things that reach out to
OL,10,Fshow that person that you care.
