OL,3,C'Find the words' - the push to get
OL,4,Cpeople talking about baby loss
OL,6,F"I think perhaps one of the things not
OL,7,Fto do is to try and make the grief
OL,8,Fbetter and minimise it. One of the
OL,9,Fmost hurtful things that people can
OL,10,Fsay and parents tell us about is
OL,11,Fstarting sentences with 'at least' -
OL,12,Fit's minimising the importance and I
OL,13,Fthink people try and do it because
OL,14,Fpeople trying to make it feel not so
OL,15,Fbad or make it feel more comfortable
OL,16,Ffor themselves.
OL,18,F"If you feel you are going to say 'at
OL,19,Fleast' just stop."
